{
  "stem": "27443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was outhouses in the back of the house, with holes made in the wood that we used as outhouses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And to hide, I jumped into-- inside, and holding onto the board till the selection was over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took out a few thousand Jewish women, women and men at that time, to be killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I really don't know what made me do it and how I did it, but there was a river behind.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I jumped out from outhouse, I went into that water and washed myself as best as I could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the way I survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's the instinct that told you what to do and how to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was a young girl, and I guess when you are young, you-- it was fight to live.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a fight for survival.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all hungry and dirty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rats were eating us up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had, in our clothes-- because we had no means of washing clothes properly-- we had lice that they were so big, that we couldn't even kill them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how big they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That we used to take our clothes, when we used to come in from work-- and this was our spare time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to delouse ourselves, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because we were eaten up alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at night, we had rats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Even if you had a little bit of food or a piece of bread that you saved for next morning, the rats used to eat it up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was our life in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it came to an end when we were surrounded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
